{
  "stem": "188.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And somehow, the-- the-- the fear that you would do something that would-- that would endanger everybody.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like being seen by someone by accidentally moving a curtain.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] Somebody seeing the quantity of food that was being prepared.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had enough, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There was malnutrition because there was a lack of essentials, but we-- we never had hunger.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Being on a farm, they had their own cattle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They slaughtered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They-- And I have memories of having to help with the slaughtering of-- of a pig and being the one who had to stand with a bucket to catch the blood because sausage was made from that.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] this-- for a city girl, a child, this was-- I don't think I ever ate any of the sausage.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] And in my nightmares, which are rather frequent, I still hear a squealing pig.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] But [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the people were good to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were-- we were very fortunate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The elderly lady, the-- the grandmother of the family, would come, was a deeply religious woman who never went to church.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But she would come every night to us, and she said, I read such a beautiful little prayer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Let's pray it together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Not trying to convert us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] They were-- they were such [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] unbelievable, unbelievable people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I know that the Dutch population as a whole was not too great, and the-- the loss of Jewish life was tremendous.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My experience has really been very positive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
